      News story
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Awards success for Coal Authority and partners
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Ochre from mine water treatment schemes used to treat soil contaminated with arsenic at Mersey Gateway</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
